                <li>Be able to give concrete examples of each type of transaction cost</li>
                <li>The Boeing/Spirit case is your go-to example for make vs buy decisions</li>
                <li>Remember: high specificity/complexity/criticality → make in-house</li>
                <li>Coase theorem: firms exist because markets have transaction costs</li>
            </ul>
